        "authorId" : "24302707-9254-48df-89a5-cbcc349462b8",
        "body" : "Should be vice-versa, right?\r\n\r\nWe should first increase by 1 and in the event handler substract 1 [otherwise we can in theory go below 0, which is forbidden].\r\n\r\nAlso - the addition should go before the EventAfterDuration.",
