        "authorId" : "7a59a326-58b3-4590-b70a-297d2e27daa5",
        "body" : "Updated comments on FakeEventClock and FakeEventClock::Sleep to clearly state that restriction, and also to more clearly document the association between the FakeEventClock and its GoRoutineCounter.",
